title: Justin Rose conquers Hong Kong: Englishman outduels Dane Lucas Bjerregaard in dramatic final day
text: Golfer Justin Rose tightens grip on Hong Kong Open Justin Rose tightens his grip on the Hong Kong Open as he moves to the top of the leaderboard -- but he singled out compatriot Ian Poulter as a key rival standing between him and the trophy. On Friday night they played in a small golf course in the central district of Hong Kong.
